ion, the counter rotating vortex pair,\nand the in-hole velocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Aug 2019 17:04:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Oct 2019 18:01:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-03"}
