ing microbe to the interface, we\nmeasure a significantly enhanced force transduction at distances larger than\nthe maximum extend of the beating flagella, highlighting the importance of\nhydrodynamic interactions for scenarios in which flagellated microorganisms\nencounter surfaces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Aug 2019 19:22:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-13"}
